results.story: The Nike Dunk Low TD God of Wealth celebrates the lunar new year with a China-exclusive colorway built for little feet. Secured with no-tie elastic laces, the upper features a suede build in neutral grey and black tones. Gold satin lines the interior, while patterned brocade detailing lands on the eyestay, heel overlay, and Swoosh. Embroidered throughout the heel, amber-colored stripes reference the year of the tiger. The low-top rests on cupsole tooling that pairs a white midsole with an orange translucent rubber outsole.
